          <p class='first-para'>
            May I move Amendment No. 184, in my name?
          </p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
      
      <div class='hentry member_contribution'>
        <a name='S5LV0663P0_20040715_GCR_158'>  </a>
        <blockquote cite='http://hansard.millbanksystems.com/people/ms-patricia-hollis' class='contribution_text entry-content'>
          <a class='speech-permalink permalink' href='#S5LV0663P0_20040715_GCR_158' title='Link to this speech by Ms Patricia Hollis' rel='bookmark'>&sect;</a>
          <cite class='member author entry-title'><a href="/people/ms-patricia-hollis" title="Ms Patricia Hollis">Baroness Hollis of Heigham</a></cite>
